{
  "manifest_version": "0.2",
  "name": "hyperd-mcp",
  "display_name": "hyperD x402 APIs",
  "version": "1.0.1",
  "description": "23 x402 tools for AI agents — 16 paid HTTP endpoints + multi-call bundle settlement + watch subscription tier + 3 free meta tools. DeFi yield, wallet risk, contract audit, governance, sentiment, cross-protocol liquidation risk, wallet anomaly detection, P&L (FIFO/LIFO/HCFO), agent budget guardian. 7 chains: Base, Ethereum, Polygon, Arbitrum, Optimism, Avalanche, BNB. Pay per call in USDC on Base.",
  "long_description": "MCP server exposing the hyperD x402 paid API catalog (api.hyperd.ai) as 23 MCP tools accessible from Claude Desktop, Cursor, Cline, and Zed. Each tool call signs an EIP-3009 USDC payment authorization with the user's wallet, settles on Base mainnet via Coinbase's CDP facilitator (~2 seconds), and returns the data. No accounts, no API keys, $0.001-$0.20 USDC per call.\n\nNEW IN v1.0:\n- hyperd.bundle ($0.20 fixed): 1-10 paid GETs in ONE x402 settlement, saves up to 33% vs à la carte.\n- hyperd.wallet.pnl ($0.05): realized + unrealized P&L over a window with three cost-basis methods.\n- hyperd.liquidation.risk ($0.10): cross-protocol health factor across Aave V3 / Compound v3 / Spark / Morpho.\n- hyperd.wallet.anomaly ($0.10): behavioral deviation vs the wallet's own 180-day baseline.\n- hyperd.budget.guardian ($0.01): agent USDC spend visibility + cap check.\n- Watch subscription tier (hyperd.watch.create at $3 prepay): HMAC-signed webhook alerts on liquidation thresholds.\n\nINCLUDES: balance lookup, DeFi yield recommendations (DefiLlama), token security scoring (GoPlus), wallet risk + sanctions (Chainalysis Oracle), DEX quote aggregation (Paraswap + 0x), wallet behavioral persona, pre-trade contract audit, DAO proposal LLM summarization, Farcaster sentiment, gas oracle, multi-chain balance.\n\nWORKING AGENT IN 30 LINES: examples/python/risk_sentinel.py — forkable Python demo bundling 4 risk signals in one $0.20 settlement.",
  "author": {
    "name": "the-thomas-code",
    "url": "https://api.hyperd.ai"
  },
  "homepage": "https://api.hyperd.ai",
  "documentation": "https://www.npmjs.com/package/hyperd-mcp",
  "support": "https://github.com/hyperd-ai/hyperd-mcp/issues",
  "icon": "https://api.hyperd.ai/favicon.ico",
  "keywords": [
    "x402",
    "defi",
    "base",
    "usdc",
    "paid-apis",
    "ai-agents",
    "claude",
    "agent-tools"
  ],
  "license": "MIT",
  "server": {
    "type": "node",
    "entry_point": "dist/server.js",
    "mcp_config": {
      "command": "node",
      "args": [
        "${__dirname}/dist/server.js"
      ],
      "env": {
        "HYPERD_WALLET_PRIVATE_KEY": "${user_config.wallet_private_key}",
        "HYPERD_API_BASE": "${user_config.api_base}"
      }
    }
  },
  "tools": [
    {
      "name": "hyperd.catalog.list",
      "description": "List all available hyperD x402 API endpoints with their prices, descriptions, and example responses. FREE — no wallet required. Use this to discover what tools are available before configuring a wallet.",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {}
      },
      "annotations": {
        "title": "Catalog (free)",
        "readOnlyHint": true,
        "destructiveHint": false,
        "idempotentHint": true,
        "openWorldHint": true
      },
      "outputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "network": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "network_size": {
            "type": "integer"
          },
          "description": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "resources": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "object"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "hyperd.pricing.get",
      "description": "Get the current price list for all hyperD paid endpoints (in USDC on Base). FREE — no wallet required.",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {}
      },
      "annotations": {
        "title": "Pricing (free)",
        "readOnlyHint": true,
        "destructiveHint": false,
        "idempotentHint": true,
        "openWorldHint": true
      },
      "outputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "endpoints": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "Map of endpoint path -> { price, description }"
          },
          "currency": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "network": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "hyperd.health.check",
      "description": "Check the health of the hyperD API: which network it's on, whether the payment facilitator is configured, which optional backend keys are wired, and cache stats. FREE — no wallet required.",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {}
      },
      "annotations": {
        "title": "Health (free)",
        "readOnlyHint": true,
        "destructiveHint": false,
        "idempotentHint": true,
        "openWorldHint": true
      },
      "outputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "status": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "network": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "paymentNetwork": {
            "type": "string"
          },
