      "description": "Agent spend visibility: aggregates recent outbound USDC transfers from a wallet over a configurable window (1h/24h/7d/30d). Returns total spend, by-destination breakdown, projected-24h rate, and an optional under_cap flag if cap_usd is provided. Use BEFORE initiating the next paid x402 call to enforce a self-imposed budget. Bridged USDC.e variants are NOT counted. Costs $0.01 in USDC.",
